🗂️ SMB (Server Message Block): A network protocol used for file sharing, printer access, and inter-process communication over a network.
Port Number: 445

#smb-os-discovery

It Gather: OS & Version (e.g., Windows 6.1 - Windows 7), Samba Version (if the target is running Samba), Computer Name (NetBIOS name or hostname), System Time (current time on the remote machine)

